### Get All Sales Order Services
GET http://localhost:8080/so/api/sales-order-services
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Code: YOUR_TENANT_CODE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Get All Sales Order Services with Filters
GET http://localhost:8080/so/api/sales-order-services?sales_order_id=123&treated=false
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Code: YOUR_TENANT_CODE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Get Sales Order Service by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/so/api/sales-order-services/1
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Code: YOUR_TENANT_CODE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

